>>> Installing AWSCLI on ubuntu 24 

$ sudo apt update
$ sudo snap install aws-cli --classic
$ aws help


>>> Installing AWSCLI on ubuntu 22
$ sudo apt update
$ sudo apt install awscli -y
$ aws help
$ q

